Package: autocart
Type: Package
Title: Modified Classification and Regression Trees for Spatial Autocorrelation
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Ethan", "Ancell", email = "ethanancell@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Ethan Ancell <ethanancell@gmail.com>
Description: An implementation of the classification and regression tree (CART) algorithm
    that gives greater flexibility in modifying the splitting function. The greater
    flexibility can be used to make splits according to measures of spatial autocorrelation.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    fields,
    gstat,
    raster,
    sp
Imports:
    Rcpp
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Suggests:
    testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
VignetteBuilder: knitr
